                <p class="date">July 13, 2024:</p>
                <br>
                <p class="body">The <a href="/termsofservice">Terms of Service</a> have been updated. Changes made: All games you play on the website may become public information, including the approximate time your account was last active. The terms may be updated at any time, and it is your responsibility to make sure you're up-to-date on them.</p>
